name: Infinite Harmony Beams Set 08 with 08 Sound Percussion
description: HTML5 file is suitable for interactive art galleries. Once the page is loaded a gravity function is triggered and the bars fall up and down. One beam that touches the ground triggers a sound. Eight variations that are all executed at the same time create a calming melody composition. This is a variation/collection of eight 8/8 hmlt5audiovisual.  Press "SPACE" or "MOUSE LEFT" for replay.
